name: Long Grey String Feather
description: This hair feather is for girls or guys with long hair. It's on a grey suede chord and has reddish feathers as well as multi-colored feathers. Also features a range of colored beads. Feather piece is on a earing (you can braid small piece of hair and set in) or apon request can be put onto an alligator clip.
